Source.Name: rocthrust
Source.Summary: ROCm Thrust - run Thrust dependent software on AMD GPUs
Source.Description: Thrust is a parallel algorithm library. This library has been ported to HIP/ROCm platform, which uses the rocPRIM library. The HIP ported library works on HIP/ROCm platforms. Currently there is no CUDA backend in place.
